## Common Workflows

### Adding a New Feature

1. Create domain directory: `internal/app/users/`
2. Add models: `models.go`
3. Add repository interface and implementation: `repository.go`
4. Add service: `service.go`
5. Add HTTP handler: `handler.go`
6. Wire up in `internal/bootstrap/bootstrap.go`
7. Add routes in `cmd/api/main.go`

### Database Changes

{% if include_db -%}
1. Update schema in `db/schema/`
2. Generate migration:
```bash
mise run db:diff add_column_foo
```
3. Review SQL in `db/migrations/`
4. Apply:
```bash
mise run db:migrate
```
{% else -%}
Database not included. Set `include_db = true` when scaffolding.
{% endif -%}

### Running Tests

```bash
mise run test        # Unit tests
{% if include_e2e -%}
mise run e2e         # E2E tests
{% endif -%}
mise run lint        # Linter
```

## Mise Quick Reference

| Task | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `mise run test` | Run unit tests |
| `mise run lint` | Run golangci-lint |
| `mise run tidy` | Tidy dependencies |
| `mise run build` | Build binary |
| `mise run fmt` | Format code |
| `mise run run` | Run service locally |
{% if include_dockerfile -%}
| `mise run up` | Start infrastructure |
| `mise run down` | Stop infrastructure |
| `mise run logs` | Follow logs |
{% endif -%}
{% if include_db -%}
| `mise run db:up` | Start postgres only |
| `mise run db:migrate` | Apply migrations |
| `mise run db:status` | Show migration status |
| `mise run db:diff <name>` | Generate new migration |
| `mise run db:reset` | Reset database |
{% endif -%}
{% if include_e2e -%}
| `mise run e2e` | Run e2e tests |
| `mise run e2e:up` | Start e2e postgres |
| `mise run e2e:down` | Stop e2e postgres |
{% endif -%}
{% if include_mockery -%}
| `mise run mocks` | Generate mocks |
{% endif -%}
{% endif -%}
